<p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 15px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: black !important">近日，第十四届蓝桥杯全国软件和信息技术专业人才大赛（软件类）省赛成绩揭晓。我校共有69位参赛同学获奖，其中19位同学获一等奖入围全国总决赛，获二等奖共27人，三等奖共23人。据统计，我校学生进入国赛总人数在参赛的64所省内高校中排名第十，在高职类院校中排名第一。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em">&nbsp;</p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0pt 5.4pt" width="650" height="1513"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;width: 650px"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;height: 36px" class="firstRow"><td valign="center" width="169" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: windowtext; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: middle; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 1px;margin-left: 1px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: middle;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-align: center"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 